      "content": "\"finding relief\" or \"managing\" it... that's what the doctors say. but there is no relief. it's just a matter of how much more of this i can take before i break. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually get some peace and quiet is to just... not be here anymore. it feels like the only way to stop the burning is to just stop everything.",
